com.tombarrasso.android.wp7ui
Class WPFonts

java.lang.Object
  com.tombarrasso.android.wp7ui.WPFonts

public final class WPFonts
extends java.lang.Object

Simple class containing static references to specified fonts in the /assets/fonts/ directory. Used to set the Typeface of views ie. WPTextView WPTextView.
Currently using Vegur as a legal supplement to Microsoft's Segoe UI.
Version 1.1

  • New WPFonts.FontSet API and the ability to use different fonts.

Since:
05-17-2012
